    <string name="exercises_to_improve_control">Exercises to Improve Control</string>
    <string name="exercise_info_title">Control Improvement Exercises</string>
    <string name="exercise_info_content">## Basic Exercises\n\n
1. **Isolation Exercise**\n
   - Focus on moving one finger at a time\n
   - Practice making small, controlled movements\n
   - Repeat 10 times for each finger\n\n
2. **Grip Training**\n
   - Practice different grip types:\n
   - Light grip (holding paper)\n
   - Medium grip (water bottle)\n
   - Firm grip (stress ball)\n\n
3. **Precision Tasks**\n
   - Pick up small objects\n
   - Stack blocks\n
   - Practice writing or drawing\n\n
## Advanced Exercises\n\n
1. **Speed Control**\n
   - Vary movement speed\n
   - Practice quick and slow movements\n
   - Focus on smooth transitions\n\n
2. **Coordination**\n
   - Combined movements\n
   - Mirror natural hand movements\n
   - Practice daily tasks</string>
